casebody.data:
Grafton,

June 26, 1909. Atwood v. Burt. Eri C. Oakes, for the plaintiff. Greorge W. Pike, for the defendant.

Assumpsit. Transferred from the March term, 1909, of the superior court by Chamberlin, J., upon an agreed statement of facts. Upon the ground that the statement was insufficient, the order was,

Case discharged.
